text: Maly Utyash () is a rural locality (a village) in Zilim-Karanovsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 122 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 46 km from Krasnousolsky, 7 km from Zilim-Karanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Maly Utyash
